categorization_prompt:
Categorize the following email into one of these categories: Important, Newsletter, Spam, To-Do, Meeting, Personal.
Return a short category label and a one-sentence rationale.

Email:
{email_text}

Respond as JSON: {"category": "...", "reason": "..."}

auto_reply_prompt:
Draft an email reply based on the user's requested tone. Use the email thread context if available. If the email is a meeting request, politely ask for an agenda and propose 2 time slots.

Context:
{email_text}

User instruction:
{user_instruction}

Respond as JSON: {"subject":"...","body":"..."}
